title: Looking for team mates
body:
I'm a silver 3 adc main.
Looking for a duo queue partner & flex/norms team mates.
Located in Newcastle.

Swing me a message here or add me.

Summoner name; Australisch

replies.body: https://discord.gg/8jKcHvR try this place out, just join and say you play lol and you should be able to find people to play with
Im in S3 also, love being a supp for a good adc. ill give u an add can have a game or two some time!
It took me a moment to realise that you weren't talking about the Newcastle in England xD
